                <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-xl p-5">
                    <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L4.342 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">Frais de retrait</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                                Frais uniques pour le premier retrait de cette tontine
